name: GIFT CERTIFICATE
description:
Want to give the gift of art but don't know what painting your loved one will want? 

No problem, a gift certificate makes it easy. Purchase any amount you like, send them as gifts or save them for later. 

There are options for different amounts below, you can build your custom amount by selecting a combination of different amounts (the qty can be adjusted in the shopping cart) or you can purchase multiples to send to the whole family!

When you place your order please send me a note that includes where you would like the gift certificates sent and the total amount for each. If you send me the name of the recipient I will add it to the certificate. If you would like to add a personal note please include this as well.

Gift certificates will have a custom promo code that can be entered in the shopping cart to redeem the total amount. Once a gift certificate code is used it expires and cannot be used again.

If you have any questions or special requests please feel free to contact me.

All Gift Certificates SHIP FREE!
